🌟 Read our reviews, we have over 8,000 5 star reviews! Here are just a few ... 🌟
"These came out beautifully! Very impressed with the quality. So much better than the ones you buy at Target®‎ or Babies R Us®‎."

☂ MC This listing is for one birthstone charm.

This simple birthstone charm hangs from its own ring so it can just slip onto the chain with other pendants.

The birthstone is a channel set Swarovski crystal rimmed in silver. 

Birthstones for all twelve months are available. Please specify which birthstone you would like in the message to seller box at checkout.

♥ To add extra discs or birthstones, check out our Add On section:

♥ Please see my shop policies for current production times. Thank you!

♥ Thank you for looking!
